Basically, the Ts are trying to destroy a castle and the CTs are trying to protect it.

The Ts can win by either killing all the CTs or by planting the bomb (there will be 2 bombs each round). The bomb can be planted at the top of the castle near all the barrels. The CTs can win by killing all the Ts.

The Ts can get through the wall by either climbing one of the ropes or by breaking the main door.

****Ts****

Spawn outside of castle and wall.
Have 300 hp.
Have mp5.

****CTs****

Get to choose one of 2 classes;   Archer or Warrior.
Start at top of the castle

.  **Class: Archer**
Gets 50 hp.
Gets Scout.

.  **Class: Warrior**
Gets 150 hp.
Gets m3 (shotgun).

The CTs have 30 seconds to choose a class, if they don't choose in time, they will be killed.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If I have used one of your textures please leave a comment letting me know. The barrels at the top of the castle are from ze_lotr_helms_deep_v4_2.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ok here goes.

EDIT: Was a major bug i missed. Is now fixed.

Version name is now mg_piratewars_extended_fixed

-------------------------------------------------------

mg_piratewars_extended_fixed

-------------------------------------------------------

This map is simply an extension of the original mg_piratewars.

It looks very similar but is very different in terms of gameplay. 

Full list of changes below:

-------------------------------------------------------

- Pirate ships now take an average of 2 hits to an area before it breaks, also on the first hit the area will become a physics prop before breaking on the 2nd hit.

- Pirate ships no longer sink. Instead, when the damage is great enough to the overall ship, all areas will become physics props and the ship will fall to pieces.

- Cannons on areas that have been hit and turned to physics props will be disabled after 20 seconds.

- Cannonsballs now kill if they hit a player directly.

- Life boats now have unlimited hp (Due to popular demand)

- Life boats now have ladders on either side to assist players who are attmepting to climb on board after falling into the water.

- Treasure chests can now be found on the bottom deck of the ships. On rare occasion this chest holds a compact pistol with 1 clip. (May spawn on both ships in one round)

- Crows nest now added on the smaller sail of each ship. In the crows nest you will find a cannon. The crows nest/sail can take 3 hits before turning into a physics prop.

- Every player must now pick up a knife at the exit to the spawn at the start of each round. The first knife gives the player who picks it up 'Captain Status'. The captain gives all players of his team an HP regeneration buff. Therefore staying near by and protecting the captain is advised. 

- Both life boats and cannons are now activated by pressing 'use' (Deafult E) on them. To activate the cannon push E at its base, for the boats push E on the rudder handle.

- 1 or 2 textures have been changed to make it look a tiny bit nicer. Nothing special though in terms of the looks. 

-------------------------------------------------------

I hope you enjoy my final ever map and i hope to see you all playing soon.

Goodbye, forever :)

_sText:
mgpharaohstomb_fix
==================
- This is a _course_ map which I've been working on for quite a while, and I'm finally going to go ahead and release it. I'd consider this map hard for _some_ people.
- Some traps were inspired by other mappers, _all_ of which were credited accordingly.
- This map is intended for _66 tick_ servers. (For those that still use 100+..)
- Obviously, a **Noblock** plugin is required..
-  Map allows respawn **_for the first ten minutes_**.
  -  Map supports the [AutoRespawn](http://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?p=905786 "AutoRespawn") plugin for that duration. (I _highly_ suggest you use it.)
     - **For the servers that do not choose to use it, when you die, join spectate and then join the Terrorist team again.**
  - I also suggest you use a dissolve plugin, one such as this: [Dissolve](http://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=71084 "Dissolve").
- **Thank you for downloading and playing!**
- **If there are any problems, please let me know.**

_fix Changes
==================

- The screenshots have not been updated as there were very little to no visual changes at the points at which I took the original screenshots. 
 - Music is now controlled by the Music Volume slider in the Audio Options.
 - The map is overall _a tiny bit_ easier.
     - The 7 second trap is now 8 seconds.
     - Replaced the random doors with a different trap.
     - The first two holes at the low gravity fall are a little bigger, and the last block before it is also bigger.
 - Changed the teleport method used at the longjumps. (To fix a flaw.)
 - Reduced the lag at the wind part.
 - Other small fixes and changes..

_aChangeLog.text: Fixed unintended ways to complete some traps.
Removed custom particles as they didn't work as I'd liked.

mg_pauls_teambattle_v2
#######################

This map is all about teamwork and completing the maps as a team as fast as possible. This map requires TEAMWORK if you want your team to beat the opposing one!

10 stages for each team to complete

#Surf
#Ball Path
#Water Climb
#Knife Path
#Strafe
#Climb
#Soccer
#Race
#Death Drop
#Targets

First team to complete all 10 before the other team wins! Simple!

Map Specific details:

#Surf - Pretty easy surf, get to the end platform to complete.

#Ball Path - Guide the ball to the end of the map. Best stratergy is to make a wall around the path whilst one person pushes.

#Water Climb - hold SPACE and CROUCH all the way around. Get to the end to complete.

#Knife Path - Each block has 400hp, best stratergy is to get all your teammates here to rush through it. Get to the end to complete.

#Strafe - follows from mg_ aztec_strafes map, get through the holes and land in the dumpster to complete.

#Climb - Climb to the end to win. Note: Theres a Shortcut in this map.

#Soccer - Score 2 goals to complete.

#Race - Race to the end to complete.

#Death Drop - Dodge all the obstacles to complete.

#Targets - Each target has 200hp, Get all your teammates there to speed it up. Ammo at the back. Kill all 12 targets to complete.


#######
CHANGE LOG
#######
V1
- Bugs fixed.

Thannk, hope you enjoy!

V2
- Made the surf level easier.

V3
- Deagle Bug fix. Players can no longer use deagles to kill players if they manage to get it out of the targets level. (From what Ive tested)
- Fixed linux crash bug.
